# Deployment Guide — Nercy Centeno Portfolio

## Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 18.17+ (recommended: 20+)
- npm 9+

### Local Development

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm run dev

# Open http://localhost:3000
```

### Production Build

```bash
# Build for production
npm run build

# Start production server
npm start
```

