## Post-Deployment Checklist

### SEO
- [ ] Submit sitemap to Google Search Console (`/sitemap.xml`)
- [ ] Verify structured data with Google Rich Results Test
- [ ] Test Open Graph with Facebook Sharing Debugger
- [ ] Test Twitter Cards with Twitter Card Validator
- [ ] Submit to Bing Webmaster Tools

### Performance
- [ ] Run Lighthouse audit (target: 95+ all categories)
- [ ] Test mobile responsiveness on multiple devices
- [ ] Verify all animations are smooth (60fps)
- [ ] Check Core Web Vitals in Google PageSpeed Insights

### Content
- [ ] Replace placeholder testimonials with verified references
- [ ] Add real project screenshots to case studies
- [ ] Upload a professional OG image (`/public/og-image.png`)
- [ ] Add certification details to resume section
- [ ] Set up Calendly integration for discovery calls
- [ ] Connect contact form to email service (e.g., Formspree, Resend)

### Analytics
- [ ] Set up Google Analytics 4
- [ ] Set up Vercel Analytics (if using Vercel)
- [ ] Configure lead tracking events

### Security
- [ ] Verify HTTPS is enabled
- [ ] Check security headers are applied
- [ ] Test CSP (Content Security Policy) if needed

