## Customization Guide

### Updating Content
All content is centralized in `src/lib/data.ts`. Update this file to change:
- Personal information
- Hero section text
- About section story
- Skills and expertise
- Project case studies
- Timeline entries
- Testimonials
- AI assistant knowledge base

### Adding Blog Posts
Create new markdown files in `src/content/blog/` (blog engine architecture is ready for extension).

### Replacing Screenshots
Add project screenshots to `public/images/projects/` and update the projects section components.

### Calendly Integration
Replace the LinkedIn scheduling link in the contact section with your Calendly embed URL.

